6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Marketmuse and NovelAI share a solid foundation of core features including Long Form. Where Marketmuse pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Seo Tools and Templates and Api Access and Team Collaboration, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, NovelAI uniquely offers Short Form and Tone Control, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Marketmuse holds an overall score of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 5/10, while NovelAI scores 7/10 overall and 5/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, NovelAI comes in at a lower starting price of $10/mo, while Marketmuse begins at $149/mo. Marketmuse has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. NovelAI does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
